    dc:creator "Kluge, Nikita; Sivaruban, T.; Srinivasan, Pandiarajan; Barathy, S.; Isack, Rajasekaran" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Diagnosis, variability, distribution and systematic position of Labiobaetis pulchellus (Müller-Liebenau & Hubbard 1985) (Ephemeroptera, Baetidae, Baetis s. l.)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836232>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836234>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836230>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836250> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836232>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–16. Labiobaetis pulchellus, larva. 13, labrum; 14–15, left and right mandibles; 16, labium. Abbreviations: a–d, submarginal arc of setae (a, central seta; b–c, first two setae after central seta); ats, apical tuft of setae on mola)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7836232/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836234>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–26. Labiobaetis pulchellus. 17, hypopharynx with superlingua; 18, maxilla; 19–26, half of larval metathorax with hind protopteron and hind wing of the same individual with the same magnification: 19–20 and 21–22, two males from India; 23–24, male from Sri Lanka; 25–26, female from Sri Lanka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7836234/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836230>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–12. Labiobaetis pulchellus, larva. 1–10, larval exuviae: 1, head; 2, 5, thorax with legs; 3, 6, 9, half of pronotum and mesonotum; 4, 7–8, 10, abdomen and caudalii (1–4, specimen from Karnataka, India; 5–8 and 9–10, two specimens from Sri Lanka; 11–12, larvae from India)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7836230/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836250>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56–60. Labiobaetis pulchellus, genitalia of male imagines (56, non-reared specimen from Madurai; 57, reared specimen from Uva; 58–59, reared specimen from Madurai; 60, reared specimen from Karnataka)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7836250/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

